<h2>Customers</h2>

<p>This is a map of the number of customers in each postcode sector of Leeds. Data from <a href="https://northernpowergrid.opendatasoft.com/explore/embed/dataset/lct-datasets-ps-upload/custom/">Northern Powergrid</a></p>

